Global Heat Press Market Insights
Heat Press Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Heat Press Market Overview
The global heat press market size was valued at USD 1.9 billion in 2023 and is expected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.1% from 2024 to 2030. The growing adoption of heat press machines in the textile, promotional products, and customized goods industries is driving market growth. The increasing demand for high-quality, durable printing solutions for apparel and other products is also supporting the market expansion. The market is highly fragmented with various manufacturers offering different types of heat presses catering to a wide range of applications.

